title: Michelle Wie West & Wale Ogunleye on PlayersTV
itunes:title: Michelle Wie West & Wale Ogunleye on PlayersTV
description:
Michael Barr, Mike Lynch, and Scarlet Fu speak with LPGA golfer Michelle Wie West, and Wale Ogunleye, NFL veteran and Head of Sports and Entertainment at UBS, about PlayersTV, an athlete-owned and culture-powered media and entertainment network home to a diverse collection of original series, co-produced by athletes and brand partners.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
